Package org.husky.emed.ch.models.document

Class EmedDocumentDigest

java.lang.Object
org.husky.emed.ch.models.document.EmedDocumentDigest
Direct Known Subclasses:
EmedDisDocumentDigest, EmedMtpDocumentDigest, EmedPadvDocumentDigest, EmedPmlcDocumentDigest, EmedPmlDocumentDigest, EmedPreDocumentDigest
public abstract class EmedDocumentDigest extends Object
Represents the digest of an Emed document. This class is declined in subclasses EmedMtpDocumentDigest, EmedPreDocumentDigest, EmedDisDocumentDigest, EmedPadvDocumentDigest, EmedPmlDocumentDigest and EmedPmlcDocumentDigest.

Creating these digests is typically done from a CDA-CH-EMED document with the digesters.

Author:
Quentin Ligier
